      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**Fase 2 del roadmap** (§3.3/§3.4): panel pendiente de Grafana Loki + Alloy.\n\nHasta entonces, forense puntual vía:\n\n- `GET /api/v1/logs?app=$app` (API del core)\n- `journalctl -u streamhub-core` / `docker compose logs -f core`\n- `streamhub_log_events_total{source,level}` (puente log→métrica, panel en server-global.json)"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {},
        "overrides": []
